Hardware Audit — April 15, 2026
Fresh findings from on-device testing. All items below are new or updated.
Crashes

Text tool crashes immediately — adds a white rectangle then crashes. Do not ship. Fix or cut.
Stroke vanishes mid-stroke under heavy Apple Pencil pressure — affects brush, eraser, all shape tools. Likely a pressure value overflow or NaN entering the render pipeline. HIGH PRIORITY.

Brush & Stroke

Brush size breaks rendering — at large brush sizes, strokes behave incorrectly across all tools. Root cause unknown. Needs investigation before the pressure issue can be fully isolated.
Pressure sensitivity on eraser — may not be necessary. Consider removing pressure from the eraser path entirely and using fixed pressure = 1.0. Simplifies the failure surface.
Shape tool stroke thinning on release — brush, circle, box, and line tools all show a thinner stroke on release than during the drag. Last segment is rendering at a lower pressure. Known issue, needs tail-taper fix or pressure clamp on final segment.
Paint tool white halo around strokes — premultiplied alpha issue on the brush composite pipeline. Already partially addressed in compositor blend factors (April 15) but still visible on device.

Selection Tools

Rectangle select pixel offset ~20px upward — when moving or deleting a selection, the affected content is ~20px above the actual selection box. Likely a coordinate mismatch in the extract/clear/render pipeline under the new polygon-based marquee. Must fix before ship.
Lasso select is slow — functional but takes noticeably long. The CPU-side point-in-polygon loop over potentially millions of pixels is the bottleneck. Consider bounding box pre-filter or GPU acceleration.
Copy/paste selection to new layer — MISSING. When rect select or lasso is active, add a "Copy to New Layer" action alongside the existing Delete button. Extracts selected pixels into a brand new layer without clearing the original. High value, low risk.

Tools That Don't Work

Eyedropper — tapping canvas does not update brush color. Should be straightforward — read pixel at tap location from the composite texture and set as current color.
Image import — opens photo gallery but imported image does not appear on canvas. Must place on its own new layer on import. Fix or cut.
Text tool — crashes. Fix or cut for TestFlight.

Move Tool (Pointer / 4-Arrow)

Overcomplicated UX — currently adds a full rectangular select over the entire layer which feels wrong. Intent is simpler: select the move tool, drag to reposition all pixels on the current layer. No marquee needed. Simplify to layer-drag only.

UI / Layout

Onboarding keyboard pushes fields off screen — "Let's Set Up Your Canvas" form gets squashed when the software keyboard appears. Needs ScrollView + keyboard-aware layout or .ignoresSafeArea(.keyboard) adjustment.
Canvas size percentage indicator hidden behind gallery icon — move the zoom percentage readout into the toolbar. It should always be visible.
AI feedback history panel goes off screen — needs scroll + correct sizing in the expanded panel. Should default to most recent feedback on open, not empty state.

Tools to Cut (Redundant)

Rotate Left / Rotate Right toolbar buttons — redundant now that pinch-rotate works well on device. Remove both. Recenter button stays.


